# Smarty templates

## Path resolution

- `|@vtemplate_path` resolves a template name against the current skin + module fallback chain.
- `|@vtemplate_path:$QUALIFIED_MODULE` resolves against a specific module (use for cross-module includes).

## Common directives

- Inherit layout:  `{extends file="MainLayout.tpl"|@vtemplate_path}`
- Include partial: `{include file='EditHeader.tpl'|@vtemplate_path:$QUALIFIED_MODULE}`
- Render dynamic template: `{include file=$STEP_TEMPLATE|@vtemplate_path:$QUALIFIED_MODULE}`
- Translate label: `{vtranslate('LBL_FOO', $MODULE)}`

## Controller ↔ template

- Pass variables: `$viewer->assign('NAME', $value);`
- Render: `$viewer->view('Edit.tpl', $qualifiedModuleName);`
- AJAX/modal views: render fragment only — do NOT `extends MainLayout.tpl`.

For full-page views missing the menu/header, see `main-layout-views.mdc`.
